STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff,
v.
Joshua M. GAUDETTE, a/k/a Josh Ramirez, Defendant. State of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Mario Vega, Defendant-Petitioner. C-984 September Term 2017
080723 Supreme Court of New Jersey. June 22, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-2629/2643-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
